Spotify HTML & CSS Clone

This project is a simple front-end clone of the Spotify web player, built using only HTML and CSS. The goal is to replicate the look and feel of the Spotify interface while focusing on design and layout techniques.

Features

Responsive design

Navigation bar similar to Spotify

Sidebar with playlist options

Main content area with album covers and song lists

Footer music player

Technologies Used

HTML5

CSS3 (including Flexbox and Grid)
